        <description>&lt;hr /&gt;&#13;
&lt;h3&gt;Allow Name to match on FQDN (Patch)&lt;/h3&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;When identifying endpoints by any method that includes matching on FQDN, if this system property is set to true then a CI may also be considered a match if the "name" field in the CMDB matches the FQDN from Tanium.&lt;br /&gt;&#13;
&lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;strong&gt;Default&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;i&gt;true&lt;/i&gt;</description>
